          "name": "What is position sizing?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Position sizing is how much you buy/sell so your loss at the stop loss equals your chosen risk amount. It helps control risk consistently."
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "What is a good risk per trade?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
